  %7 = bitcast i64* %sum to i8*
  %8 = call i8* @llvm.hyper.lookup(i8* nonnull %7, i64 8, i8* bitcast (void (i8*)* @zero to i8*), i8* bitcast (void (i8*, i8*)* @plus to i8*))
